- **Monochromatic Palette**: Red (#E50000), Grey (#E0E0E0), Black (#0A0A0A)
- **Glassmorphism Sidebars**: Backdrop blur effects (Coming in Phase 6)
- **Advanced Code Blocks**: Dual-color borders with gradient backgrounds âœ…
- **Unified Callout System**: Card Elevated style with 3D lift effects âœ…
- **Color-Coded Lists**: 4-level ordered & unordered markers âœ…
- **Gradient Tables**: Markdown & Dataview tables with red headers âœ…
- **Horizontal Rules**: Minimalist red separator lines âœ…
- **Performance-Optimized**: Zero animations, smooth CSS transitions only
- **Clean CSS**: No !important flags, proper specificity hierarchy

## ğŸ“¦ Installation

1. Download theme files
2. Place in `.obsidian/themes/pur3v4d3r-imperial/`
3. Open Obsidian Settings â†’ Appearance â†’ Themes
4. Select "Pur3v4d3r Imperial"
5. Restart Obsidian

