## ğŸ¨ Tag Color Categories

The theme includes automatic color-coding for common tag types:

- **Red** (Bright): `#project`, `#task`, `#todo`, `#active`
- **Grey** (Status): `#status`, `#in-progress`, `#done`, `#seedling`, `#evergreen`, `#reference`
- **Dark Red** (Priority): `#urgent`, `#important`, `#high-priority`, `#critical`
- **Dark Grey** (Reference): `#source`, `#citation`, `#library`, `#book/`
- **Light Grey** (Concepts): `#concept`, `#idea`, `#theory`, `#learning/`, `#meta`, `#system`
- **Black** (Archive): `#archive`, `#completed`, `#deprecated`

Nested tags (`#parent/child`) automatically display smaller.

